    <abstract>
      <t>   Composite ML-DSA defines combinations of ML-DSA with RSA, ECDSA, and
   EdDSA.  This document specifies the conventions for using Composite
   ML-DSA algorithms within the Cryptographic Message Syntax (CMS).

